# ============================================================
# XDC Multi-Client Port Standard
# ============================================================
# Generated from XDC-ROADMAP-2026 Phase 1
# Issue: https://github.com/XDCIndia/xdc-node-setup/issues/82
#
# Formula:
#   Apothem = Mainnet + offset
#   RPC/WS/AuthRPC/Metrics/SkyOne: +100
#   P2P/Discovery: +10
# ============================================================

# --- GP5 (go-ethereum XDC) ---
